ports to spread the message of what's happening back home,\\\" he explained.\", \"from\": 3472, \"to\": 3552, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 3478, \"to\": 3484}, {\"ngram\": \"the message\", \"from\": 3495, \"to\": 3506}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Highlighting the lack of resources, the two-time Olympian remarked, \\\"I am privileged, but we do not even have a pool in Palestine.\", \"from\": 3554, \"to\": 3684, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3603, \"end\": 3611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999953524821, \"rank\": 4.647620336530218e-09, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 3674, \"end\": 3683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"score\": 0.9999999150250042, \"rank\": 8.497478101784139e-08, \"text\": \"Palestine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lack\", \"from\": 3567, \"to\": 3575}, {\"ngram\": \"resources\", \"from\": 3579, \"to\": 3588}, {\"ngram\": \"a pool\", \"from\": 3664, \"to\": 3670}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having two Olympic swimmers without a pool is a success.\", \"from\": 3685, \"to\": 3741, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two Olympic swimmers\", \"from\": 3692, \"to\": 3712}, {\"ngram\": \"a pool\", \"from\": 3721, \"to\": 3727}, {\"ngram\": \"a success\", \"from\": 3731, \"to\": 3740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It shows that if we are given opportunities, we will take them.\", \"from\": 3742, \"to\": 3805, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"opportunities\", \"from\": 3772, \"to\": 3785}]}, {\"sentence\": \"People back home have nothing, yet when given a chance, we excel.\\\"\", \"from\": 3806, \"to\": 3872, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 3806, \"to\": 3812}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 3828, \"to\": 3835}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 3852, \"to\": 3860}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I just want to stop people suffering' The swimmer reflected on the harsh realities Palestinians face as the war continues.\", \"from\": 3876, \"to\": 4000, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3961, \"end\": 3973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 0.9999657815403457, \"rank\": 3.4219568340323573e-05, \"text\": \"Palestinians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3897, \"to\": 3903}, {\"ngram\": \"The swimmer\", \"from\": 3915, \"to\": 3926}, {\"ngram\": \"the harsh realities\", \"from\": 3940, \"to\": 3959}, {\"ngram\": \"the war\", \"from\": 3981, \"to\": 3988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I saw a video of a baby's corpse dragged by a dog.\", \"from\": 4002, \"to\": 4053, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a video\", \"from\": 4009, \"to\": 4016}, {\"ngram\": \"a baby's corpse\", \"from\": 4020, \"to\": 4035}, {\"ngram\": \"a dog\", \"from\": 4047, \"to\": 4052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How can you play sports after that?\", \"from\": 4054, \"to\": 4089, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 4071, \"to\": 4077}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We see these atrocities, and it's hard, but we are here to do what we can for our country,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 4090, \"to\": 4190, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these atrocities\", \"from\": 4097, \"to\": 4113}, {\"ngram\": \"our country\", \"from\": 4168, \"to\": 4179}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just want people to stop suffering,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 4192, \"to\": 4241, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 4205, \"to\": 4211}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not complicated.\", \"from\": 4242, \"to\": 4264, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We want to be alive and have basic human rights.\", \"from\": 4265, \"to\": 4313, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"basic human rights\", \"from\": 4294, \"to\": 4312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some of my people do not even dream of equal rights.\", \"from\": 4314, \"to\": 4366, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my people\", \"from\": 4322, \"to\": 4331}, {\"ngram\": \"equal rights\", \"from\": 4353, \"to\": 4365}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's too far-fetched.\\\"\", \"from\": 4367, \"to\": 4389, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 28-year-old is passionate about his SwimHope Palestine project, aimed at preventing drownings.\", \"from\": 4391, \"to\": 4489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his SwimHope Palestine project\", \"from\": 4427, \"to\": 4457}, {\"ngram\": \"drownings\", \"from\": 4479, \"to\": 4488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In Gaza, many children drown near the ocean.\", \"from\": 4491, \"to\": 4536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4495, \"end\": 4499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"score\": 0.9853396635876427, \"rank\": 0.014878459635916165, \"text\": \"Gaza\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many children\", \"from\": 4501, \"to\": 4514}, {\"ngram\": \"the ocean\", \"from\": 4526, \"to\": 4535}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We aim to set up temporary pools and teach basic swimming skills to counter this,\\\" explained al-Bawwab.\", \"from\": 4537, \"to\": 4640, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"temporary pools\", \"from\": 4554, \"to\": 4569}, {\"ngram\": \"basic swimming skills\", \"from\": 4580, \"to\": 4601}, {\"ngram\": \"al-Bawwab\", \"from\": 4630, \"to\": 4639}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Kids from Gaza ask how to become Olympic swimmers.\", \"from\": 4642, \"to\": 4693, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4653, \"end\": 4657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"score\": 0.9853396635876427, \"rank\": 0.014878459635916165, \"text\": \"Gaza\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kids\", \"from\": 4643, \"to\": 4647}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic swimmers\", \"from\": 4676, \"to\": 4692}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Without pools or nutrition, what do I tell them?\\\"\", \"from\": 4694, \"to\": 4743, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pools\", \"from\": 4702, \"to\": 4707}, {\"ngram\": \"nutrition\", \"from\": 4711, \"to\": 4720}]}, {\"sentence\": \"lamented al-Bawwab.\", \"from\": 4744, \"to\": 4763, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"lamented al-Bawwab\", \"from\": 4744, \"to\": 4762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Right now, I just want kids to be alive and dream.\", \"from\": 4764, \"to\": 4815, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 4788, \"to\": 4792}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eventually, I hope we will have infrastructure to support education and sports.\\\"\", \"from\": 4816, \"to\": 4896, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"infrastructure\", \"from\": 4848, \"to\": 4862}, {\"ngram\": \"education\", \"from\": 4874, \"to\": 4883}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 4888, \"to\": 4894}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If I see 10,000 people dead on my phone, it's numbing.\", \"from\": 4898, \"to\": 4953, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"10,000 people\", \"from\": 4908, \"to\": 4921}, {\"ngram\": \"my phone\", \"from\": 4930, \"to\": 4938}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If others saw the same about their country, they'd go berserk,\\\" he concluded with a sobering thought: \\\"It's an honor to be here, representing 15 million people without a recognized country,\\\" acknowledged al-Bawwab.\", \