 members\", \"from\": 7351, \"to\": 7373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have had teammates die.\", \"from\": 7379, \"to\": 7404, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"teammates\", \"from\": 7390, \"to\": 7399}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been horrible for all of us,\\\" she shared how her loved ones have had to endure unimaginable loss and hardship.\", \"from\": 7405, \"to\": 7520, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 7435, \"to\": 7437}, {\"ngram\": \"her loved ones\", \"from\": 7455, \"to\": 7469}, {\"ngram\": \"unimaginable loss\", \"from\": 7489, \"to\": 7506}, {\"ngram\": \"hardship\", \"from\": 7511, \"to\": 7519}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It seems like every single day we have to go through getting phone calls of our friends or family who passed away.\", \"from\": 7522, \"to\": 7637, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"phone calls\", \"from\": 7584, \"to\": 7595}, {\"ngram\": \"our friends\", \"from\": 7599, \"to\": 7610}, {\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 7614, \"to\": 7620}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even since we have been here, stuff like that has happened and it's all the more reason for us to raise the flag,\\\" Tarazi added.\", \"from\": 7638, \"to\": 7766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"stuff\", \"from\": 7668, \"to\": 7673}, {\"ngram\": \"all the more reason\", \"from\": 7706, \"to\": 7725}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 7730, \"to\": 7732}, {\"ngram\": \"the flag\", \"from\": 7742, \"to\": 7750}, {\"ngram\": \"Tarazi\", \"from\": 7753, \"to\": 7759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The swimmer also explained the cultural significance of her the dress she wore at the opening ceremony and how it has added another layer to her Olympic experience.\", \"from\": 7768, \"to\": 7932, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The swimmer\", \"from\": 7768, \"to\": 7779}, {\"ngram\": \"the cultural significance\", \"from\": 7795, \"to\": 7820}, {\"ngram\": \"the dress\", \"from\": 7828, \"to\": 7837}, {\"n